{"tid":651751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教聯指一開始「母語教學」已是不對，應要「中文教學」。","createTime":"2018-05-03T10:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T11:11:35.000Z","uid":53060,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"26fe1f0e8a04bf328a0f338ffa74dd96b4b4fe13","tid":651751,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180503/s00001/64a23b03d31896284e0c5758d26da6ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180503%2Fs00001%2F64a23b03d31896284e0c5758d26da6ae.jpg&h=d2039cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局在網上教學資源頁面上載一篇學者文章，文中稱粵語不符「母語」之義，只是方言，引發爭論。教聯會會長黃均瑜亦形容<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>粵語只是「方言」</strong></span>，直指<span style=\"color: red;\">「一開始都說（香港）母語教學是不對」，應是「中文教學」。</span><br />\n<br />\n黃均瑜早上在商台節目表示，「廣東人來說，粵語當然是母語，但香港不止指廣東人架嘛」。他解釋說，「粵語」是「廣府話」，是廣州附近地方方言，「如果廣州附近地方，（粵語）就是母語，但你潮州人，母語就是潮州話，我們香港還有百多萬福建人，母語就是福建話&hellip;&hellip;所以一開始都說，<span style=\"color: red;\">（香港）母語教學是不對的，是否福建人來，我就要以福建話教呢？應該是中文教學，便用中文去教囉」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n黃均瑜又說，香港方言就是用粵語，「這只是方言，方言廣東省還可以的，但<span style=\"color: red;\">去到全國，那你這個就不通&hellip;&hellip;要看到定位及作用</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n教協組織部主任田方澤則說「粵語當然是母語」，而香港教育大多數學生能用流利廣東話，「社會近幾十年都習慣用粵語，教學應傾重這語言」。他表示，不同社會環境對「方言」有不同定義，「現在你說粵語是方言，某程度上無錯，但無必要糾纏在這方面」，強調應珍惜廣東話及其背後文化。"},{"pid":"ff029500a0246a13d5945dcd5d259e5d3363b870","tid":651751,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180503/s00001/1525310303319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180503%2Fs00001%2F1525310303319&d=7EB62gZsKTrwMWa9SY97DP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=86e77efc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180503%2Fs00001%2F1525310303319&h=53335fcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180503/s00001/1525310303319</a>"},{"pid":"932fa658193d0b0c615cc55a14b6338a99200a33","tid":651751,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/182638_9facebf337d11a0b93debe0210b01a41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F182638_9facebf337d11a0b93debe0210b01a41.png&h=a2324b45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主所有post都係反粵語同制造港台仇恨"},{"pid":"c01ae4d5a49800b8d56204aecac2b8bc0e18a549","tid":651751,"uid":41292,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:30:06.000Z","msg":"已經分唔清邊啲係五毛邊啲係引人注意嘅on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d9dd5f67ca6ef221ae2effa9e5beca63c05bf6","tid":651751,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:31:28.000Z","msg":"奶共教聯會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa118c196db6422b3a933a628646775af68b266","tid":651751,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4ae9fb32edd178d08e216aaa8004fed22d02d9","tid":651751,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:33:50.000Z","msg":"撐國教23條　教聯會黃均瑜選人大<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171120/20219715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171120%2F20219715&d=7EB62gZsKTrwMWa9SY97DP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=445c056a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171120%2F20219715&h=0218d788\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171120/20219715</a>"},{"pid":"f458cf19f050ef521bf10d0e976a98b8231c4090","tid":651751,"uid":54832,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"中你老母<br />\n<br />\n根本由細到大都應該英文教所有課程<br />\n另增設粵語科 繁體中文科"},{"pid":"033b62f0d29aca75bb1a2b9434056fc3bd2e6781","tid":651751,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:35:45.000Z","msg":"你老母講乜話呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151e6cb6dd292627f4e224ac6b22e3c93e38546c","tid":651751,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:59:38.000Z","msg":"條友知唔知中國所有語言+方言。都係叫中文? <br />\n中共都要政治正確。指普通話係國家標準漢語。係標準漢語。唔係標準中文呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條柒頭真係柒到出汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大陸D大學。唔係叫中文系㗎。係叫漢語系。就係大陸都要強調，漢語唔係中文的唯一。<br />\n<br />\n中文教學? 乜香港有教埋中國所有口語+文字咩?"},{"pid":"ed3222d5aead8d929b81b062ec520d2a1a9c1e00","tid":651751,"uid":56699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"要英文教學"},{"pid":"c0d407d5943e8bbddeb37f98cf2bd398d270b669","tid":651751,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"香港人俾人撚狗咁撚，自作孽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeae9b32c34dc3b0df12d90d01633212dbc260d9","tid":651751,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:06:54.000Z","msg":"其實呢d撚樣係到廢up大陸有冇人聽到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老鼠曾講就多人知姐，呢d廢柴尻up都冇高層知啦"},{"pid":"698f9fce03c3634ca17b5cf5c10e7e36389caf02","tid":651751,"uid":153239,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 母語教學係對香港人講架wo<br />\n你自已分自已做潮洲老唔認自已係香港人<br />\n將自已分離開去 關人撚事<img src=\"/asse